    &lt;&lt; Theory of operation of find/change &gt;&gt; (leoFind.py)
    &lt;&lt; Key bindings, an overview &gt;&gt; (leoKeys.py)
    &lt;&lt; about 'internal' bindings &gt;&gt; (leoKeys.py)
